nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROBLEM TWO COMPARTMENT ORAL $DATA pk_oral2_30_90.csv IGNORE=# $INPUT ID TIME AMT DV MDV $SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4
$PK CL = THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) ;CL/F V2 = THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2)) ;V2/F Q = THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3)) ;Q/F V3 = THETA(4)*EXP(ETA(4)) ;V3/F KA = THETA(5)*EXP(ETA(5)) ;Absorption rate constant ALAG1 = THETA(6)*EXP(ETA(6)) ;Lag time
$ERROR IPRED = F W = SQRT(THETA(7)**2 + THETA(8)**2 * IPRED**2); additive plus proportional error model IRES = DV - IPRED IWRES = IRES / W Y = IPRED + W * EPS(1)
$THETA (0,100);CL (0,700);V2 (0,70) ;Q (0,500);V3 (0,10) ;KA (0,1) ;ALAG1 0 FIX 0.01 FIX
$OMEGA .25 ;CL .25 ;V2 1 ;Q .25 ;V3 .25 ;KA .25 ;ALAG1
$SIGMA 1 FIX ;ERRCV
;$ESTIMATION METHOD=1 POSTHOC MAXEVAL=9999 PRINT=5 $ESTIMATION NOABORT MAXEVAL=9999 METHOD=1 INTER PRINT=10 SIGDIGITS=3
$COVARIANCE PRINT=E
$TABLE ID TIME IPRED IWRES DV NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=sdtab4403 $TABLE ID CL V2 Q V3 KA ALAG1 NOPRINT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND FILE=patab4403
